03-06-2011 12:53:15.343584 [DEBUG] stat(160003384)

原来是因为：

int setattr_send_request(struct file_stat * stat_arr)                                                  
||     main                   |{   
                              |    DBG();
-  mds_conn.c (/home/ning/idni|    struct setattr_request * req = setattr_request_new();                                              
|-   variable                 |    struct setattr_response * response = setattr_response_new();                                       
||     pool                   |    
|                             |    struct file_stat * t = EVTAG_ARRAY_ADD(req, stat_arr);                                             
|-   function                 |    EVTAG_ASSIGN(t, ino, t-> ino); // 不然它不认..                                                     
||     ping_cb                |    EVTAG_ASSIGN(t, size , t-> size); // 不然它不认..                                                  
||     stat_cb                |    
||     ls_cb                  |    
||     mknod_cb               |    EVRPC_MAKE_REQUEST(rpc_stat, pool, req, response,  setattr_cb, NULL); 

明明是setattr,却发送 stat命令..
在匆忙状态下写的代码，就是糟糕哟.

